				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				You need to use a &quot;small piece of Velium&quot; looks like the red clay bricks and is stackable. These drop pretty regular off the miners in the Crystal Caves. A pain to run over and back but they are an easy kill. Once you hand the small piece to Handor in the Razors Edge he will give you the pick back and you take it back to the guy in the tunnels.
